<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>名人 - 人物</title><link>https://siftrss.com/f/LbvpaQbPYJQ</link><description>来自人物的最新名人新闻、采访和故事。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 12:28:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>约瑟夫表弟的妻子肯德拉也被捕后，艾米·杜格·金泪流满面：“我不知道发生了什么事”</title><link>https://people.com/amy-duggar-king-breaks-down-in-tears-after-cousin-joseph-duggar-wife-kendra-also-arrested-11931607</link><description>据阿肯色州当局称，这对夫妇面临四项危害未成年人福利罪和四项非法监禁罪，而约瑟夫还被指控涉嫌在佛罗里达州度假时猥亵一名 9 岁女孩。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/r95cohT6A-MJH_ls7CjISj06xcg=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Amy-Duggar-King-Kendra-and-Joseph-Duggar-032126-f704e1c63ed7455aa34a274dbc68f1fe.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Mar 2026 18:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/amy-duggar-king-breaks-down-in-tears-after-cousin-joseph-duggar-wife-kendra-also-arrested-11931607</guid></item><item><title>雅诗士丹利是谁？关于贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake) 酒后驾车被捕视频中的女性，您需要了解什么</title><link>https://people.com/who-is-estee-stanley-all-about-woman-in-justin-timberlake-dwi-arrest-footage-11931609</link><description>这位由造型师转型为设计师的设计师是汀布莱克和他的妻子杰西卡·贝尔 (Jessica Biel) 的老朋友&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/vqSJt4Uy0W7IARyNvXN6rjV5ff0=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Estee-Stanley-032126-fab270bbb9a54599a5ebe947005c1433.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Mar 2026 17:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/who-is-estee-stanley-all-about-woman-in-justin-timberlake-dwi-arrest-footage-11931609</guid></item><item><title>肯德拉·杜加尔 (Kendra Duggar) 与丈夫约瑟夫 (Joseph Joseph) 一起因儿童危害指控被指控数小时后出狱</title><link>https://people.com/kendra-duggar-seen-leaving-jail-hours-after-charged-alongside-husband-joseph-duggar-11931586</link><description>这对夫妇因据称发生在 2020 年的一起事件而